layouts.Name: The Beast FPO - Nokia Disc Golf Park
layouts.Notes:
Out of Bounds (806.02): Marked by WHITE lines and stakes. This applies to any line marked in this manner even if not explicitly mentioned on a specific hole. 

Relief Area (806.04): Marked by BLUE lines and stakes.
